This is a placeholder file. To create an actual Excel example, create a file with the following structure:

Column A: Camera Name (optional)
Column B: IP Address (optional)  
Column C: Branch Name (required)
Column D: Phone Number (optional)

Example data:
| A         | B             | C     | D           |
|-----------|---------------|-------|-------------|
| كاميرا 1  | 192.168.1.1   | فرع 1 | 01234567890 |
| كاميرا 2  | 192.168.1.2   | فرع 2 | 01123456789 |
| كاميرا 3  | 192.168.1.3   | فرع 3 | 01098765432 |
|           | 192.168.1.4   | فرع 4 | 01555555555 |

Note: 
- Only Column C (Branch Name) is required
- The system will skip duplicate branch names if the option is selected
- Camera names and IP addresses are optional but will be stored if provided
